# Reproducible Docker builds — never ship local state.

# Node / pnpm / package caches
**/node_modules
**/.pnpm-store
.pnpm-debug.log
npm-debug.log*

# Build outputs (Dockerfile rebuilds from source)
**/dist
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Workspace state (this is what `AIPE_SPACE` points at — never bake it in)
.aipehub
.aipehub-*
**/.aipehub
**/.aipehub-*

# Editor / OS noise
.DS_Store
.idea
.vscode
*.swp

# Git
.git
.gitignore
.github

# Tests / extras. NOTE: examples/ must NOT be ignored — examples/* are
# pnpm workspace importers, and `pnpm install --frozen-lockfile` refuses
# a lockfile whose importers aren't all present in the build context.
templates
python-sdk
docs
*.md
CHANGELOG.md
CONTRIBUTING.md
SECURITY.md
LICENSE-NOTICES*.md

# Coverage / debug
coverage
.nyc_output
*.log

# Local secrets (defence in depth — these should never be in the repo anyway)
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
runtime/secret.key
